Title: The Causes and Consequences of Wal-Mart's Growth
Abstract: Wal-Mart is the largest company in the world, yet little is known about 
its economic impact. This essay discusses what is known about Wal-Mart's competitive
advantage and its economic impact on local communities, as well as the national and 
global economy, and highlights the open questions to be addressed by future research.
